    "# Spatio-Temporal Predictive Analytics Benchmark\n",
    "\n",
    "Demonstrates the techniques behind:\n",
    "> *\"Predictive analytics precision +22% using geospatial features and transformer temporal encoders\"*\n",
    "\n",
    "**What this does:**\n",
    "1. Generates realistic spatio-temporal event data (incidents with lat/lon + timestamps)\n",
    "2. Engineers geospatial features (geohash, H3 hex, sinusoidal spatial encoding, spatial context)\n",
    "3. Engineers temporal features (cyclical time encoding, temporal context)\n",
    "4. Builds a transformer-based temporal sequence encoder\n",
    "5. Compares: Raw lat/lon baseline → + Geospatial features → + Temporal encoder → Full pipeline\n",
    "6. Shows precision improvement from each technique\n",
    "\n",
    "**Runtime:** ~3 minutes, CPU only"
   ]
